                    "name": "Tangle Spores",
                    "type": "stat_block_section",
                    "text": "A creature bitten by a cythnigot becomes afflicted by fast-growing spores that swiftly grow into twitching spikes and hideous pallid growths of hairlike fibers. These growths erupt from the bite wound and writhe and wrap around the creature's limbs. <a aonid=\"125\" game-obj=\"Traits\">Plant</a> creatures take a \u20132 circumstance penalty to save against tangle spores; <b>Saving Throw</b> DC 17 Fortitude; <b>Maximum Duration</b> 6 rounds; <b>Stage 1</b> <a aonid=\"3\" game-obj=\"Conditions\">clumsy 1</a> (1 round); <b>Stage 2</b> clumsy 1 and <a aonid=\"16\" game-obj=\"Conditions\">flat-footed</a> (1 round); <b>Stage 3</b> clumsy 2, flat-footed, and if you attempt a <a aonid=\"104\" game-obj=\"Traits\">manipulate</a> action, you must succeed at a DC 5 flat check or it's lost; roll the check after spending the action, but before any effects are applied (1 round).",
